table_caption: Mean cortical thickness for temporal regions of interest (in mm) for the control and subjective cognitive decline (SCD) groups.
table_foot: Between-group comparisons indicate decreased cortical thickness in SCD in left and right entorhinal cortices and the right temporal pole. *p < 0.05 and **p < 0.01. & There were 327 participants over the age of 55 with anatomical T1w images available. Two control participants and three SCD participants were excluded from the cortical thickness and brain structure volume analyses due to segmentation errors, for a total of 322 segmentations as detailed in this table.
